724454f-a.text:
375 West End Avenue, on S.W. corner of 78th Street, an apartment house built about 1913. The houses adjoining on 78th Street are the original buildings on the site, but not built till after 1891.
The other half of the West End Avenue side of the block, down to 77th Street, will be demolished in July 1924 to make room for another apartment building.
About 1923.
Gift of E. W. Jenks.
